caption.title: EV71-specific cell mediated immune responses induced by the formalin-inactivated EV71 vaccine with diverse adjuvants.
caption.p: Splenocytes from vaccinated mice were isolated and stimulated with the EV71 vaccine strain. Supernatants of splenocytes were harvested at 48 h after stimulation and analyzed for cytokine levels using a multiplex system. Graphs show means + SEMs. * p < 0.01, using one-way ANOVA with Tukeyâ€™s post-hoc test.
